<p>
I am a student of physics at the university of cologne, in the middle of my master’s thesis. Currently I am interested in the bulk boundary correspondence of higher order topological insulators and the K-theoretic description thereof. 
</p>

<p style="margin-top: 10px">
During the literature research for my bachelor' s thesis, I encountered numerous pay walls and membership restrictions. Although the university has contracts with the various institutes and publishers, it still adds a level of annoyance. As much as I do understand the need for proper payment, I myself believe that science has to be available for everyone. 
For that reason I have decided to upload the notes that have seen enough care to have proper (enough) citation.
